The Company prioritizes workforce health and safety by:

•	Implementing comprehensive safety protocols;
•	Providing regular training programs, and fostering a strong safety culture;
•	Conducting risk assessments, ensuring compliance with occupational health and safety regulations; and
•	Continuously monitoring and improving safety practices.

